//www.open-encyclopedia-system.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">Open Encyclopedia System website</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The OES Demo encyclopaedia consists of an editorial layer (WordPress Plugin) to administrate and edit content or configure OES features, a website (WordPress Theme) to display the content and an exemplary data model including sample data. The OES framework can be used to realise a customised online reference work. See&nbsp;<a href=\"http://oes01.cedis.fu-berlin.de:8089/about/about-oes-demo/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"625\">About OES Demo</a>&nbsp;on different ways to use the OES Demo application.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong>&nbsp; The sole purpose of articles on prominent works of reference (section&nbsp;<em><a href=\"http://oes01.cedis.fu-berlin.de:8089/t_demo_article_type/reference-works/\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"18\">Articles:Reference Works</a></em>) and related data is to provide content for the sample encylopaedia, whereas articles in the section&nbsp;<a href=\"http://oes01.cedis.fu-berlin.de:8089/t_demo_article_type/oes-application/\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"19\"><em>Articles:OES Applications</em>&nbsp;</a> describe current applications of the OES framework. &nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":717,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://oes01.cedis.fu-berlin.de:8089/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/oes_frontpage33-1024x871.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-717\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"container\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1,\"className\":\"oes-content-table-header1\"} -->\n<h1 class=\"oes-content-table-header1\" id=\"oes-applications\">OES Applications</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Several online reference works are realised using the OES framework, ranging from online encyclopaedia to online handbook. Click on the links below to access their websites or read more about the OES applications in our exemplary&nbsp;<a href=\"http://oes01.cedis.fu-berlin.de:8089/t_demo_article_type/oes-application/\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"19\">articles</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"oes-demo-card-container\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group oes-demo-card-container\"><!-- wp:oes/oes-card {\"oes_card_title\":\"ComDeG\",\"oes_card_body\":\"Online-Compendium deutsch-griechischen Verflechtungen\",\"oes_card_image\":\"http://oes01.cedis.fu-berlin.de:8089/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/oes_comdeg.png\",\"oes_card_link\":\"https://comdeg.eu/\",\"oes_card_link_text\":\"comdeg.eu\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:oes/oes-card {\"oes_card_title\":\"Compendium heroicum\",\"oes_card_body\":\"Das Online-Lexikon des Sonderforschungsbereichs 948 „Helden – Heroisierungen – Heroismen“\",\"oes_card_image\":\"http://oes01.cedis.fu-berlin.de:8089/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/oes_compendium_heroicum.png\",\"oes_card_link\":\"https://www.compendium-heroicum.de/\",\"oes_card_link_text\":\"compendium-heroicum.de\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:oes/oes-card {\"oes_card_title\":\"Eiserner Vorhang\",\"oes_card_body\":\"Tödliche Fluchten und Rechtsbeugungen\",\"oes_card_image\":\"http://oes01.cedis.fu-berlin.de:8089/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/oes_eiserner_vorhang.png\",\"oes_card_link\":\"https://todesopfer.eiserner-vorhang.de/\",\"oes_card_link_text\":\"todesopfer.eiserner-vorhang.de\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:oes/oes-card {\"oes_card_title\":\"B.forscht!\",\"oes_card_body\":\"Projektbrowser für Altertumswissenschaften in Berlin-Brandenburg\",\"oes